:"Inspect affected UBERON terms and determine required ontology changes","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Edit checked-out term stanzas and check changes back into uberon-edit.obo","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Validate ontology syntax and relevant identifiers/metadata","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"Commit only intended edited files locally","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Create uncommitted ISSUE_COMMENTS.md and PR_COMMENTS.md","status":"pending","priority":"medium"}],"truncated":false},"title":"3 todos","time":{"start":1778975922647,"end":1778975922653}},"id":"prt_e333a4cab0010r284X7x5krtZ4","sessionID":"ses_1ccc74650ffeuPhztNvH8x7LBy","messageID":"msg_e333a375a001P5UxS1G3VWdUCl"}}
