{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778976036296,"sessionID":"ses_1ccc74650ffeuPhztNvH8x7LBy","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_KA5uE77N2JSaqtBBsenSzpol","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Updated `UBERON:0000379` tracheal mucosa so its logical definition is restricted to mucosa part of trachea rather than mucosa part of respiratory airway. I also checked for a hard-coded `UBERON:0001826` nasal cavity mucosa subclass edge and did not find one.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+This change fixes the inferred parent-child relationship reported in issue #3617 by narrowing the logical definition of `UBERON:0000379` tracheal mucosa.\n+\n+## Changes\n+\n+- Updated the text definition of `UBERON:0000379` from \"A mucosa that is part of a respiratory airway\" to \"A mucosa that is part of a trachea\".\n+- Updated the logical definition from `intersection_of: part_of UBERON:0001005 ! respiratory airway` to `intersection_of: part_of UBERON:0003126 ! trachea`.\n+- Checked for a hard-coded `UBERON:0001826` nasal cavity mucosa subclass relationship to tracheal mucosa and did not find one.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The prior equivalence used the broad grouping class `UBERON:0001005` respiratory airway, which could infer other airway-associated mucosae, such as nasal cavity mucosa, under tracheal mucosa. Restricting the differentia to `UBERON:0003126` trachea aligns the textual and logical definitions with the term name and intended meaning.\n+\n+## Validation\n+\n+- Confirmed `UBERON:0003126` is the existing trachea term.\n+- Checked the updated `UBERON:0000379` stanza after check-in.\n+- Ran `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o /tmp/opencode/uberon-edit-validation.obo` successfully.\n+- Ran `robot reason --input src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo --reasoner ELK --output /tmp/opencode/uberon-edit-reasoned.owl` successfully.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- [x] Read imported issue context.\n+- [x] Inspected the affected tracheal mucosa and nasal cavity mucosa stanzas.\n+- [x] Made the minimal ontology edit through term checkout/check-in.\n+- [x] Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n+- [x] Validated syntax and ELK reasoning.\n+\n+@dragon-ai-agent\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Updated `UBERON:0000379` tracheal mucosa so its logical definition is restricted to mucosa part of trachea rather than mucosa part of respiratory airway. I also checked for a hard-coded `UBERON:0001826` nasal cavity mucosa subclass edge and did not find one.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,30 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+This change fixes the inferred parent-child relationship reported in issue #3617 by narrowing the logical definition of `UBERON:0000379` tracheal mucosa.\n+\n+## Changes\n+\n+- Updated the text definition of `UBERON:0000379` from \"A mucosa that is part of a respiratory airway\" to \"A mucosa that is part of a trachea\".\n+- Updated the logical definition from `intersection_of: part_of UBERON:0001005 ! respiratory airway` to `intersection_of: part_of UBERON:0003126 ! trachea`.\n+- Checked for a hard-coded `UBERON:0001826` nasal cavity mucosa subclass relationship to tracheal mucosa and did not find one.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The prior equivalence used the broad grouping class `UBERON:0001005` respiratory airway, which could infer other airway-associated mucosae, such as nasal cavity mucosa, under tracheal mucosa. Restricting the differentia to `UBERON:0003126` trachea aligns the textual and logical definitions with the term name and intended meaning.\n+\n+## Validation\n+\n+- Confirmed `UBERON:0003126` is the existing trachea term.\n+- Checked the updated `UBERON:0000379` stanza after check-in.\n+- Ran `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o /tmp/opencode/uberon-edit-validation.obo` successfully.\n+- Ran `robot reason --input src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo --reasoner ELK --output /tmp/opencode/uberon-edit-reasoned.owl` successfully.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- [x] Read imported issue context.\n+- [x] Inspected the affected tracheal mucosa and nasal cavity mucosa stanzas.\n+- [x] Made the minimal ontology edit through term checkout/check-in.\n+- [x] Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n+- [x] Validated syntax and ELK reasoning.\n+\n+@dragon-ai-agent\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Updated `UBERON:0000379` tracheal mucosa so its logical definition is restricted to mucosa part of trachea rather than mucosa part of respiratory airway. I also checked for a hard-coded `UBERON:0001826` nasal cavity mucosa subclass edge and did not find one.\n","additions":3,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","r